name: The hardest routine happens in the locker room
description: Attending class was finally worth it, two months of craving this moment. I don't think there is nothing in the world I care less about than zumba but I do anything for this delicious instructor. I'm so thirsty and I think my neck is going to be stiff from watching us fuck. Are they about to close? Please wait one more hour. I think I'm hearing people moaning next to us anyway, it seems to me that we're not the only ones enjoying ourselves.
